    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite MRL 5 requirements, the assessment team determined that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility for regulatory submission under Low assurance level given the Monte Carlo UQ results and PIV validation comparisons. Six factors remain not-assessed but are flagged for remediation in the next assessment cycle. Provenance chain traces from the primary claim through the PIV comparison validation result and the UQ dataset to foundational experimental evidence.",
